11 likes, 0 comments - themendingmuse on March 1, 2020: "Having fun with Ms.Deborah Presley.Part 1
Deb is Elvis Presley's First daughter and former wife of Christian Brando.

She is an amazing singer, songwriter and the list of her talents goes on and on plus she is one of my dearest friends. 
Watch for her book coming out soon.
 Hey it's not about her it's about the goats and she loves our goats.
The Mending Muse goats.
 Watch for the fun video she did for us ;)
Chicago we have the goats Deb is talking of, book your event today and feel the therapeutic, fun effects of our kids.
